      Sarasota Serulneck
      March 12 ·

      Since the world is lowkey chaotic and scary right now (and since I don’t know when I’ll be back at Rice to finish this video), I‘m uploading my “Rice {Season 3}” One Second A Day to look back at some happier memories and take a minute to remember everyone who was part of making my junior year so wonderful.

      All my love to Grace Miller, Emma Alvarez, Cameron Gonzales, Alieke Feid, Gianna Policastro and Caterina Discenza - my Vitelleschi Vixens! And so so so many kisses and cin...-cins to Avery Kron, Yin Kwok, Carina Blakeley, Andy Johnson, Will Mears, and Peter Davies - literally the best abroad squad a girl could ask for. A million hugs to Carla Eastis, Christa Dawn, Jessica Waldman, Amy Clark, Claudia Michaels and Catherine Livingston for humoring my bar crawl whims and making my 21st such a great entrance into womanhood. Here’s to hopefully many more nights with my Womansion - Madison Morris, Nicole Tan, Madison Gabino, Medha Gupta, and the ever-present Oeishi Banerjee. And so much love to everyone else who puts a smile on my face in this video and in my life! I’m so so lucky to have you all and I can’t wait to make so many more memories with you ❤️

      (this video is literally potato quality I’m sorry Facebook hates high definition)
